"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-andrea-spendolini-sirieix-b1175057.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix has said she did not even want to alive in the wake of the Tokyo Olympics after finishing outside the medals in the 10metre platform diving competition.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spendolini-Sirieix had a poor second dive in Tuesday's final and then was never really in contention in her quest for asecond medal after bronze in the synchro competitioneventually finishing in sixth place.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 19-year-old was tearful in the aftermath saying she felt lucky to be alive and competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 734, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999849360394, \"rank\": 1.5063856204474077e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told the BBC: \\\"Obviously it wasn't the result that I wanted.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9162843177285891, \"rank\": 0.06127894726631377, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not even upset with the competition.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The girls dove amazing.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They dove better than me today and it's because they work really hard.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not even upset with my performance.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago, I did not even want to be alive, so today I am just happy that I am alive, I am breathing and I have got my family to support me.\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mum told me to just keep smiling and she said she was proud of me and they were here to see me.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the end of the day, that's all I can ask for,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so happy to be here, to be at theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a really long year and it does not take away from my accomplishments this year.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just missing out on one medal does not change who I am.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was just God's way of saying there is more to do and I just give God all the glory.\\\"\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after 